      "writtenOn": "2019-06-19T06:31:10Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "Prefer AutoLock versus explicitly locking:\n\nwhile (true) {\n  int rc \u003d play();\n  \n  AutoLock lock(mLock);\n  if (rc || mPlayConfig.looping) {\n    mRunning \u003d false;\n    break;\n  }\n}",
