        "id": 1233742
      },
      "writtenOn": "2019-06-19T06:31:10Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "I think there\u0027s a deadlock here, which I addressed in my other comment for this block.  Would it be possible to add unittests in a follow-up CL?  There\u0027s the start of one here: https://android-review.googlesource.com/c/platform/external/qemu/+/984778/7/android/android-emu/android/mp4/MP4Dataset_test.cpp\n\nThe deadlock would be:\n\nT1: calls stop(), setting mRunning to false\nT1: calls play(), notices mRunning is false, so it calls mWorkerThread.reset() under lock.  This  waits for the previous thread to exit\nT2: In workerThreadFunc after noticing mRunning\u003dfalse, tries to acquire mLock after play() returns\n\n(No action is required in this CL)",
      "range": {
        "startLine": 1385,
        "startChar": 8,
        "endLine": 1385,
        "endChar": 87
      },
